# Zoom-Out Product Tooltip

A modern **pure CSS animated tooltip** component designed for product catalog interfaces.  
This component uses a smooth **zoom-out interaction transition** to reveal additional information without requiring any JavaScript.

The tooltip is fully responsive, keyboard accessible, and customizable using CSS custom properties for animation timing, easing, and scaling.

---

## Features

- Pure HTML & CSS implementation
- Smooth zoom-out tooltip animation
- Zero JavaScript dependency
- Responsive product catalog friendly design
- Keyboard accessible using focus states
- Customizable animation parameters using CSS variables
- Modern UI aesthetic suitable for e-commerce interfaces

---

## Usage

Add the tooltip inside any interactive element:

```html
<button class="buy-btn">
    BUY NOW
    <span class="tooltip">Buy this product now</span>
</button>

